<materialsCitation box="[151,895,1772,1797]" location="New Brunswick" pageId="289" pageNumber="290" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="New Brunswick">
The species is only known from the 
<typeStatus box="[545,592,1773,1797]" pageId="289" pageNumber="290">type</typeStatus>
locality in 
<collectingRegion box="[715,895,1772,1796]" country="Canada" name="New Brunswick" pageId="289" pageNumber="290">New Brunswick</collectingRegion>
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
